
Overview of noun rider

The noun rider has 4 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (11) rider -- (a traveler who actively rides an animal (as a horse or camel))
2. (2) rider -- (a clause that is appended to a legislative bill)
3. rider -- (a traveler who actively rides a vehicle (as a bicycle or motorcycle))
4. passenger, rider -- (a traveler riding in a vehicle (a boat or bus or car or plane or train etc) who is not operating it)
